data.description: Three bedroom twin home tucked away in Souderton School District will be hitting the market soon!  This home needs some TLC, but is priced to sell!! The potential here is amazing, so make sure you look at comparable sold properties in the same neighborhood.  The exterior is vinyl siding and offers a large covered porch, private driveway and front entry garage.  A large living room welcomes you into the home and adjoins the dining room with ceramic tiled floor.  The kitchen has plenty of counter and cabinet space!  Relax by the fire in the family room that showcases a brick surround and raised heart.  Sliding doors lead to your private, flat, fenced in yard.  The paver patio needs some leveling, but could be brought back to life!  All three bedrooms are spacious and the owner's suite boasts a large walk-in closet with organizers.  Access the bathroom from the hallway & owner's suite.  The lower level has some drywall and is waiting to be finished.  Here you will also find the laundry room.  The one car garage completes this home a has lots of extra storage in the attic space provided.
